headline: Two Reasons to Like Lennox (and One Not So Much)
summary: Lennox has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 14.7%. The stock now trades at $614.31, marking a 25.1% gain. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
